; Date: 2024-12-27
; Updated: Relaxed filters for backtesting
; Optimized for: EURGBP (Euro/British Pound)
; Timeframe: H4 (4-Hour)
; Strategy: Mean-Reversion (S/R + RSI)
; Risk Level: Medium
